//Input time in minutes and covert it in to valid hours and minutes

int main()
{
    int min,h,minute;
    printf("\n Enter the minutes:");
    scanf("\n %i",&min);
    h=min/60;
    minute=min%60;
    printf("\n Hours=%d and Minutes=%i",h,minute);
}


Output:
Enter the minutes:
70
 Hours=1 and Minutes=10

Reference:https://funcodepro.blogspot.com/2018/12/how-to-convert-minutes-into-hours-and.html
